{"tid":1810710,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"科大強行移走民女像","createTime":"2020-01-04T06:06:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T06:48:49.000Z","uid":138707,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0fe893d2418db4489deae359a1607bd15a6291a5","tid":1810710,"uid":138707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T06:06:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200104/FDKRV6VYOILEWAIQGTI65GEE7Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200104%2FFDKRV6VYOILEWAIQGTI65GEE7Y%2F&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDpgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=a5d2f28c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200104%2FFDKRV6VYOILEWAIQGTI65GEE7Y%2F&h=241a9fef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200104/FDKRV6VYOILEWAIQGTI65GEE7Y/</a><br />\n【本報訊】科技大學學生會前晚將反修例運動民主女神像，擺放在校園內的連接橋上，隨即遭校方以「未批准」為由用木版圍封，並下令昨日下午5時前搬走，更一度流傳校方會強行清拆雕像，引起學生不滿。至昨日限期過後，校方即派保安將雕像搬至學生會接待處，學生會指摘校方拒絕與學生溝通，單方面決定移除女神像。<br />\n<br />\n因反修例活動而製作的「民主女神像」，前晚起豎立於科技大學連接橋的智慧石上，學生會稱已通知校園管理處，並招募科大民間保衞隊。惟校方得悉事件後，昨日以木板將雕像圍封，並貼出通告指雕像未經校方批准擺放在公共地方，又指雕像所顯示的訊息不代表大學立場，下令學生會昨下午5時將雕像移走。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">科大校方真係垃圾到冇人有。</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5266db9f4b72d3c015eaa34065e4a1d897b8cb6","tid":1810710,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T06:09:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82ee67c3020a873104eb9aa6a99a660046ce689f","tid":1810710,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T06:25:03.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6f73c1032c03d13081282db7d8cc97f1d8fad484","tid":1810710,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T06:48:49.000Z","msg":"陰d陰d"}]}